DEPRECATED: This form has been replaced by ai_conversation module's settings form.

The duplicate AIConversationSettingsForm in agent_evaluation has been removed
to eliminate code duplication and confusion.

Use the centralized settings form instead:
- URL: /admin/config/ai-conversation/settings
- Route: ai_conversation.settings
- Form: \Drupal\ai_conversation\Form\AIConversationSettingsForm

All AI conversation settings (AWS credentials, model selection, token limits,
operation-specific configurations) are now managed through the ai_conversation
module's settings form.

Date deprecated: February 11, 2026
To remove: Original AIConversationSettingsForm.php file

Related Changes:
- agent_evaluation.settings route removed from agent_evaluation.routing.yml
- agent_evaluation.api_service is now an alias to ai_conversation.ai_api_service
- All controllers updated to use ai_conversation services
